Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.rbalasubramanian1.model.Game
  • @Entity
public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    The Game class is used to create the game entity in the database and extends the AbstractEntity class to set an ID and version against each game record.
